* [https://forum.freecad.org/viewtopic.php?f=10&t=29542 Merging of my Link branch] (June 2018)

Finalement, la demande d'extraction et la fusion sont arrivées :
* [https://forum.freecad.org/viewtopic.php?f=27&t=38621 App::Link: the big merge], ancien fil (July 2019), [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/2350 pull request #2350] (the BIG merge), [https://github.com/realthunder/FreeCAD/tree/LinkMerge LinkMerge branch].
* [https://forum.freecad.org/viewtopic.php?f=8&t=37757 App::Link: the big merge], fil princilipal (July 2019)
